headline: Essex Announces Release and Conference Call Dates for Its Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., January 10, 2025--Essex Property Trust, Inc. (NYSE:ESS) announced today that it plans to release its fourth quarter 2024 earnings after the market closes on Tuesday, February 4, 2025. A conference call with senior management is scheduled for Wednesday, February 5, 2025 at 9:00 a.m. Pacific Time or 12:00 p.m. Eastern Time.

headline: Los Angeles Rental Housing Demand Is Soaring. Essex Property May Benefit.
summary: Southern California represents about 40% of the net operating income of real-estate investment trust Essex Property Trust.
